title: Hang Drum Jam
description:
Hang Drum Jam is a virtual version of the heavenly ethnic musical instrument Hang Drum Integral. You can use it anywhere in the street jams or enjoying headphones, Hang will always be with you and give instant sound meditation. Enjoy the freedom of sound, no longer need to carry 5 pounds with an iron in your android smartphone all that may be necessary to activate the application and play in the mountains, the sea, around the campfire or in the countryside. Go to jam with guitar sounds and other drums, as well as the sounds of synthesizers. With Hang Drum Jam you get a sound artist, create! 

-= Features =-
- Multi Touch supported!!!
- Really Hang Drum Sounds. 
- Best ethnic musical instrument Hang Drum Integral always with you.
- High quality sound samples.
- Enjoy the music .
- Use in street music jams.
- Maximum volume.
- Implemented a dynamic volume, now sound more lively.
- Added multisampling.
